  </head>

  <body
    style="width:800px; margin:50px auto;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"
  >
    <table
      style="border:1px solid #dddddd;width:100%;border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr><td
         style="text-align:center;background-image: url('{{websiteMailBgUrl}}'); background-size: cover;background-position: center;padding:10px"
        >
        <img src="{{websiteLogoUrl}}" alt="XDS-SPARK" width="150" />
        </td></tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:0 20px">
          <p style="padding-top:10px">Hi {{firstName}},</p>
          <p>Welcome to XDS Spark! We are thrilled to provide you with login credentials that give access to your <b>complimentary</b>, Foundational membership.</p>
          <p>Click <a href="{{webSiteLoginUrl}}"><u>HERE</u></a> to access the log-in page. Your email is {{email}}, and your password is {{password}}
          </p>
          <p>As a Foundational member, please update the following company info to put your best foot forward.</p>
          <ol>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">From the Home Page, go to Edit Company Profile</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">Under General Info, update your company name, services, size, logo and banner image.</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">Under About, update your company description.</li>
          </ol>
          <p><b>Please don't wait!</b> Buyers will have the ability to discover your company and view profile info.</p>
          <p><b>Interested in unlocking the next level?</b> Premium membership provides you with rich functionality to complete your full company profile, which greatly enhances your company presence to buyers. Discover project opportunities, manage lists, add your company to upcoming events, and seek out other Service Providers to partner with.</p>
          <p>Also note that the Premium tier provides you with <b>four (4) user licenses</b> that you can assign to your colleagues.</p>
          <p><b>To upgrade to Premium</b>, select Subscription Details in the main menu, and go from there!</p>
          <p>For more info on Premium features and pricing, check out our website at <a href="{{websiteUrl}}"><u>xds-spark.com.</u></a></p>
          <p>We ask that you please not share your login credentials outside of your organization.</p>
          <p>Cheers,</p>
          <p>Your friends at XDS Spark</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
